reviews.review_text: Great AUD of classic show! The merits of this show are all so well established, it hardly needs me to add anything to the lore.  However, what is noteworthy here is the quality of this AUDacious recording.  It is appropriate this recording of a show that was meant to celebrate the Winterland lets you feel the auditorium space like no other.  You can literally feel the acoustic space with all its ambient reverb and audience vibe.  Don't get me wrong I have been a big fan of the crispy SBD mixed to perfection.  But this recording gives me something else altogether.  It helps me tap into an embodied experience of 3D acoustic space heightened by the communal outpouring of audience emotion all around me.  In the last two years of COVID restrictions, I really appreciate reminders of what it was like to feel live music.  Great work in stitching this beauty together! Thanks to all the hidden sound engineers (the usual suspects) who had a hand in making this AUD happen.
